                     <div class="prose max-w-none">
                        <p class="text-gray-500"><strong>Effective Date:</strong> September 1, 2025</p>
                        <p>This Privacy Policy describes how CrowdZero ("we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, and discloses your personal information when you visit or make a purchase from our website, crowdzero.com (the "Site"). This page provides a clear, navigable overview of our practices. You can use the navigation on the left to jump to specific topics of interest.</p>
