                    <section id="section-1" class="policy-section space-y-4">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold border-b pb-2 text-gray-900">1. Information We Collect</h2>
                        <div class="prose max-w-none text-gray-600">
                           <p>We collect information from you when you interact with our Site to provide and improve our service. This information falls into two main categories:</p>
                           <ul>
                               <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> When you make a purchase or attempt to make a purchase, we collect certain information from you, including your name, billing address, shipping address, payment information (including credit card numbers), email address, and phone number. This is referred to as "Order Information."</li>
                               <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> When you visit the Site, we automatically collect certain information about your device, including your web browser, IP address, time zone, and some of the cookies that are installed on your device. Additionally, as you browse the Site, we collect information about the individual web pages or products that you view, what websites or search terms referred you to the Site, and information about how you interact with the Site. This is referred to as "Device Information."</li>
                           </ul>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section id="section-2" class="policy-section space-y-4">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold border-b pb-2 text-gray-900">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                        <div class="prose max-w-none text-gray-600">
                            <p>We use the information we collect for various purposes, all aimed at providing a better, safer experience for you:</p>
                            <ul>
                               <li><strong>Processing Orders:</strong> To fulfill any orders placed through the Site (including processing your payment information, arranging for shipping, and providing you with invoices and order confirmations).</li>
                               <li><strong>Communication:</strong> To communicate with you about your order, products, services, and promotions.</li>
                               <li><strong>Improving the Site:</strong> To screen for potential risk and fraud (in particular, your IP address), and more generally to improve and optimize our Site (for example, by generating analytics about how our customers browse and interact with the Site, and to assess the success of our marketing and advertising campaigns).</li>
                               <li><strong>Personalization:</strong> To personalize your shopping experience and present products and offers tailored to your interests.</li>
                               <li><strong>Marketing:</strong> To provide you with targeted advertisements or marketing communications we believe may be of interest to you.</li>
                           </ul>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section id="section-3" class="policy-section space-y-4">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold border-b pb-2 text-gray-900">3. Sharing Your Personal Information</h2>
                         <div class="prose max-w-none text-gray-600">
                           <p>We share your Personal Information with trusted third parties to help us use your Personal Information, as described above. We do not sell your data. Examples include:</p>
                           <ul>
                               <li>We use a payment processor to handle transactions and shipping companies to deliver your orders.</li>
                               <li>We may also share your information to comply with applicable laws and regulations, to respond to a subpoena, search warrant, or other lawful request for information we receive, or to otherwise protect our rights.</li>
                           </ul>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section id="section-4" class="policy-section space-y-4">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold border-b pb-2 text-gray-900">4. Your Rights</h2>
                        <div class="prose max-w-none text-gray-600">
                           <p>If you are a resident of certain regions, you have the right to access the personal information we hold about you and to ask that your personal information be corrected, updated, or deleted. If you would like to exercise this right, please contact us using the contact information below.</p>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section id="section-5" class="policy-section space-y-4">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold border-b pb-2 text-gray-900">5. Data Security</h2>
                        <div class="prose max-w-none text-gray-600">
                            <p>We take reasonable steps to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no internet transmission or electronic storage method is 100% secure. We cannot guarantee the absolute security of your personal information.</p>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section id="section-6" class="policy-section space-y-4">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold border-b pb-2 text-gray-900">6. Cookies</h2>
                        <div class="prose max-w-none text-gray-600">
                            <p>The Site uses "cookies" to help us understand how you use the Site and to improve your browsing experience. You can choose to set your web browser to refuse cookies, or to alert you when cookies are being sent. If you do so, note that some parts of the Site may not function properly.</p>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                    
                    <section id="section-7" class="policy-section space-y-4">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold border-b pb-2 text-gray-900">7. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
                        <div class="prose max-w-none text-gray-600">
                            <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time in order to reflect, for example, changes to our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.</p>
                        </div>
